Load Balancer: Used to increase responsivness and spread traffic accross the cluster of services

1. It provides analytics to the admin
2. Also checks the health of the server using heartbeat
3. distribution of  traffic could be based on
    a) Depending on weights
    b)Low response time
    c)Least number of connections
    d)Round robin
    e)IP Hash
4. To further increase responsivness add Load balancers at app servers and db level


Is load balancer single point of failure?
-Yes, but we can configure Active Active or Active passive cluster

A cluster can have active active load balancer or active passive load balancers that serves the traffic


